      "title": "Crude comments and concern: Online incivility's effect on risk perceptions of emerging technologies",
      "abstract": "All correspondence regarding this manuscript should be addressed to the ﬁrst author in the Center for Climate ChangeCommunication, George Mason University, Mail Stop 6A8, 4400 University Drive, Fairfax, VA, 22030ph: 703-993-8368;e-mail: aander24@gmu.edu.This material is based upon work supported by a grant from the National Science Foundation to the UW-MadisonNanoscale Science and Engineering Center in Templated Synthesis and Assembly at the Nanoscale (Grant No. SES-DMR-0832760).Anyopinions,ﬁndings,andconclusionsorrecommendationsexpressedinthismaterialarethoseoftheauthorsand do not necessarily reﬂect the views of the National Science Foundation."
